The paper deals with the optimization of age-of-information (AoI) in wireless multiaccess channels, which involves information theory (cs.IT), networking (cs.NI), and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also proposes a decentralized status update scheme, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA).
